item.title: What Really Drives Career Growth in Data Analytics
item.description:
Career growth in data analytics is often misunderstood.
In this episode of The Lights On Data Show, George Firican and Albert Bellamy explore what actually influences career progression, from resumes and LinkedIn profiles to interviews, impact, and mindset.

A practical, experience based conversation for data analytics professionals thinking about their next move.
